### Account Service (port 5001) - internal service
### Normally called only by the Gateway. These requests are for direct testing.
### When auth is enabled, the internal token header is required (see commit: security).

@account = http://localhost:5001

### Health
GET {{account}}/health

### Apply a transaction (idempotent by transactionId == originating eventId)
POST {{account}}/accounts/acct-123/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "evt-001",
  "type": "CREDIT",
  "amount": 150.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T14:02:11Z"
}

### Apply the same transaction again (idempotent: returns original, 200)
POST {{account}}/accounts/acct-123/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "evt-001",
  "type": "CREDIT",
  "amount": 150.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T14:02:11Z"
}

### Get current balance
GET {{account}}/accounts/acct-123/balance

### Get account details and recent transactions
GET {{account}}/accounts/acct-123
